==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[imaginary]] [[number]]''' (''plural'' '''imaginary numbers''')

#{{complex}} A number of the form ''ai'', where ''a'' is a [[real number]] and ''i''<sup>2</sup> = &minus;1; a [[complex number]] whose [[real part]] is zero.

====Synonyms====
*[[purely imaginary number]]

